Juvenile Delta Outmigration Survival

surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta.Rd

Calculates the Sacramento Delta juvenile out migration survival

surv_juv_outmigration_sac_delta(
  delta_flow,
  avg_temp,
  perc_diversions,
  .intercept_one = -3.5,
  .intercept_two = 0.3,
  .intercept_three = -3.5,
  .delta_flow = 0.0013,
  .avg_temp = 0.386,
  .perc_diversions = -0.033,
  .medium = 1.48,
  .large = 2.223
)

Arguments

delta_flow

Variable describing delta inflow in cubic meters per second
avg_temp

Variable describing monthly mean temperature in celsius
perc_diversions

Variable describing monthly mean percent diverted
.intercept_one

Intercept for model one, source: TODO
.intercept_two

Intercept for model two, source: TODO
.intercept_three

Intercept for model three, source: TODO
.delta_flow

Coefficient for delta_flow variable, source: TODO
.avg_temp

Coefficient for avg_temp variable, source: TODO
.perc_diversions

Coefficient for perc_diversions variable, source: TODO
.medium

parameter for medium sized fish, source: Connor et al. (2004)
.large

parameter for large sized fish, source: Connor et al. (2004)

Source

IP-117068
